en-US.summary: An application that allows you to ask what fruits or vegetables are in season for a time of year or a given month.
examplePhrases: Alexa ask Seasonal Vegetables what is in season now
What is in season for spring
en-US.name: Seasonal Vegetables
en-US.description: This application takes the guesswork and constant googling out of eating seasonally. Just ask seasonal vegetables what fruits vegetables or both are ripening right now or in the future and add them to your next shopping list. Eating seasonally doesn't have to be hard, give it a try and start eating seasonally today.This application takes the guesswork and constant googling out of eating seasonally. Just ask seasonal vegetables what fruits vegetables or both are ripening right now or in the future and add them to your next shopping list. Eating seasonally doesn't have to be hard, give it a try and start eating seasonally today. It is estimated that meals travel over 1500 miles to get to our tables in the US. One gallon of fuel can produce as much as 20 lbs of CO2. We could reduce the tole our agricultural system takes on our planet by eating fruits and vegetables that are ripened in our own backyard, rather than ones harvested elsewhere in the world, shipped in, and ripened chemically. That's where Seasonal Vegetables comes in. To find out the fruits and vegetables that are seasonal to your area, all you have to do is ask. Taking the work out of eating seasonally, being healthier, and saving the planet. Just ask seasonal vegetables what fruits, vegetables or both are ripe right now or in the future and add them to your next shopping list. Eating seasonally doesn't have to be hard, give it a try and start eating seasonally today.
